{
  "stem": "4113.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He worked for the Gestapo too-- for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they put him aside and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we stood there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the other Jews where to be marched out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, the dead came in a few horse wagons from the sanitary department.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they just threw all the dead there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took them out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the rest are marched out to the train station.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My little brother started crying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, he wanted to go with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Gestapo says, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I went over to Schmatsler.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I asked him to let my little brother with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he said, no, I can't do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He's too young.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But he said, I promise you that he's not going to go [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That means he's not going to be killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They are going to Reichshof, which was a town not far from our town where there was a bigger ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They're going to go to that bigger ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My cousin, David, the tool and die maker, had his little boy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He could've stayed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But he didn't want his little boy to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So now the question was, what should we do?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Should we just go with transport and not stay?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You don't dare, you know, tell them that you don't want to stay and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So we decided that David said he's going to take his boy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he's going to take my little brother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The sight is very difficult to describe to you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's awful.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But anyway, they were all taken away and my cousin's wife with her little babies also.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as we stood there, a few minutes later a Gestapo man-- still-- his name was Hauch.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He's from Jaslo.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He wasn't from our town.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
